body:
Status Quo News

Saturday we had canceled pool and amusement park plans. So we went Sunday instead. By the time we got back I was so sore and sick with being a waddling, moving solar system that I knocked out on my sofa as soon as I sat down. Monday, I woke up with major pain and found out I over did it at the park walking, being in the sun and not drinking enough. So I spent Monday in the hospital, getting fluids and making sure the baby was okay. Today, Tuesday, I’m home and on a strict three day long bed rest order. So I’ll be finishing the status Quo chapter I was SUPPOSED to post Sunday and I’ll either post it later tonight or tomorrow afternoon.
